9ff95351a084d610","tid":2092534,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:13:35.000Z","msg":"唯一方法應該係接貨然後坐到張long到期<br />\n<br />\n利申：未睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T17:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"085f324df9a510b5e36621332ba0547b79019c64","tid":2092534,"uid":109571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc98f274e804a18d77b5658a6ce92d23f5861722","tid":2092534,"uid":241612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b89a4b7d797b5913e8c68cc9ff95351a084d610","tid":2092534,"uid":40684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"74d69f0f006d6107ca4d59c63361111fe9b9ddd7","tid":2092534,"uid":241612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:48:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:05:16.000Z","msg":"But what happens, you ask, if you are still exercised on one of the short options?<br />\n<br />\nSay the stock drops to $297 overnight, and the put options are exercised against you. You are suddenly the proud owner of 100 shares of stock at a cost of $305 per share. Yet they are selling for $297, an $8 difference. Even after subtracting your $6.72 premium, you've still lost money on the short put.<br />\n<br />\nWell don't panic. It's not a problem.<br />\n<br />\nYou first sell the shares, losing $8. Then you sell another put, 1 week out, at the new lower strike price of $297. This brings in around $6.50 (option price has gained in volatility but lost in time value). Then you buy back the short call for a cost of usually no more than 1 penny, and resell a new call at the lowered $297 strike, bringing in another $5.50 or so.<br />\n<br />\nNot only does your situation not worsen. It has improved. You had originally collected $12.60, but now your collected an additional $4.00. Congrats, you've milked your first proverbial cow."},{"pid":"99e70b131baddcdb7feb1c1c8c18dda2770786cf","tid":2092534,"uid":109571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T18:08:04.000Z","msg":"搵d &lt;$20既股試下唔得咩？好似幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84abe8f4f2ac52a96eb74660e015ce8b4e85be4b","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"paper trade我唔知可唔可以睇到按金requirement, short嘅按金會變動，越近價內要求越多，波動大又會加，好多時你想救倉，但發覺按金唔救，好頭痕。<br />\n<br />\n另一樣更重要，紙上談兵冇嗰種痛感，玩真錢玩一千同一萬感覺都唔同。玩一千玩得掂唔等如一萬玩得掂。何況紙倉。紙倉可以輸可以唔理，真倉冇得唔理。"},{"pid":"5253a158177cef82d962e3e6c9515c7ab1449faa","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"篇英文太長。冇睇。<br />\n<br />\n如果係long atm, short straddle,就係reverse butterfly, long 遠月 short近月甚至weekly. 亦可以形容為diagonal,對角，因為月份不同。<br />\n<br />\n疫症令股市波動大，好大機會走向一邊。<br />\n<br />\nlong 遠期，時間損耗慢，short近期，時間值賺得快。十分著數。好多人未必知㗎。<br />\n<br />\n做兩邊，係non directional，唔使估升跌。long short 不同月份，對沖時間值。<br />\n<br />\n可以話最重要兩個參數已經對沖。剩落嚟就係波動率同vega, 一定要有波幅，走得遠，否則會輸，第二，iv要升，如果iv跌，會輸。<br />\n<br />\n個人經驗唔好太高iv時做，iv一跌，long會縮得好快，short都補唔返，因為short weekly期權金好少，一縮，long邊虧損就形成，之後short好多次weekly都未必冚得返。"},{"pid":"2760a01e46bf99989eecfca69dc2e6b9e7c7eb78","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5253a158177cef82d962e3e6c9515c7ab1449faa","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"篇英文太長。冇睇。<b