t put.<br />\n<br />\nWell don't panic. It's not a problem.<br />\n<br />\nYou first sell the shares, losing $8. Then you sell another put, 1 week out, at the new lower strike price of $297. This brings in around $6.50 (option price has gained in volatility but lost in time value). Then you buy back the short call for a cost of usually no more than 1 penny, and resell a new call at the lowered $297 strike, bringing in another $5.50 or so.<br />\n<br />\n但係實際操作，如果我account冇 sufficient fund去接貨，  broker會幫我margin接貨(strike price $305)，然後我要自己賣翻出去($297) 定係 直接輸＄8？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:30:55.000Z","msg":"我自己冇用margin acc，其他po有師兄講過用margin 接，即刻賣出去，最後結果係蝕8元，但唔使用咁大筆錢。<br />\n<br />\n呢啲策略都有其風險，始終靠short,收入少於虧損，如果跌好多，就唔係蝕8元，但再roll down又收唔得幾多。一套策略一adjust就變樣，成日左一巴右一巴。<br />\n<br />\n我初頭以為佢疫情之下會靠波動賺錢，原來靠short 兩邊，個市咁chok, short 兩邊難度好高"},{"pid":"cca38a3449b5b49609ae9306266da4c00bb34899","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"619559a4a2c467f660b7cb7865f085d7ee9fcd45","tid":2092534,"uid":353442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd75b6d5f38cc74d1ca80c0e183542ddca9d346","tid":2092534,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1f647c17ca87de68c24b1bbd94e730e128af3d5","tid":2092534,"uid":241612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:07:58.000Z","msg":"用真錢嘅話就應該用Firstrade好啲<br />\n真離岸，IB都係會比港共搞到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"其實如果用FT齋做short side又叻到唔駛接貨，係咪冇成本賺錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"傻啦，其實你掉轉諗都可以話做long本小利大，賺一次夠輸好多次。<br />\n<br />\nlong short係相對又互補，short食時間值但係如果急升急跌，好短時間已經輸好大數。<br />\n<br />\n食時間值要睇長線，幾年嚟講係著數，同埋股票長線係升，short put長線係得嘅。"},{"pid":"9f1ba1b7c6fea5c8ce2b6b4b92dc4df892ea4b63","tid":2092534,"uid":109571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0372358ef323167b8c446f6320a57d1f78a331