":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:51:52.000Z","msg":"Options: When This Happens, The Market Falls 3% 13 Out of 14 Times.<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5XsZIpnpB-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5XsZIpnpB-w&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=07f6003b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5XsZIpnpB-w</a><br />\n我推介大家睇下simpler trading john carter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe2487bd7f2ad110328b051b9ae20cd3b5d1754","tid":2092534,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84abe8f4f2ac52a96eb74660e015ce8b4e85be4b","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T02:12:48.000Z","msg":"paper trade我唔知可唔可以睇到按金requirement, short嘅按金會變動，越近價內要求越多，波動大又會加，好多時你想救倉，但發覺按金唔救，好頭痕。<br />\n<br />\n另一樣更重要，紙上談兵冇嗰種痛感，玩真錢玩一千同一萬感覺都唔同。玩一千玩得掂唔等如一萬玩得掂。何況紙倉。紙倉可以輸可以唔理，真倉冇得唔理。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"我自己用TD<br />\n通常佢係send order 之前會有一個pop up window<br />\n入面會寫左扣幾多buying power 同margin"},{"pid":"eeea44a94c3b3f3a85278aa11ae8c0aba1588ea2","tid":2092534,"uid":353442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cca38a3449b5b49609ae9306266da4c00bb34899","tid":2092534,"uid":308853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"619559a4a2c467f660b7cb7865f085d7ee9fcd45","tid":2092534,"uid":353442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dd75b6d5f38cc74d1ca80c0e183542ddca9d346","tid":2092534,"uid":35393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T01:14:20.000Z","msg":"其實如果用FT齋做short side又叻到唔駛接貨，係咪冇成本賺錢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T02:38:59.000Z","msg":"傻啦，其實你掉轉諗都可以話做long本小利大，賺一次夠輸好多次。<br />\n<br />\nlong short係相對又互